dct_description_sm: ompiled & drawn especially for the Gdynia America Line Inc. by C.S. Hammond & Co.
Shows administrative divisions, cities, railroads, airline routes, canals, and distances or travel times on selected routes.
Includes inset: [Katowice, Sosnowiec] and "Facts about Poland".
On verso: Pictorial Map "Poland land of rainbow colors", diagram of Polish air service routes, col. ill. and text "Include Poland on your european tour".
